[Number of Weapons Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Setting the value above "02" will cause the game to crash once you pick up more than two weapons. Start the stage before using value "00".
Values - 
00 - No Weapons, but can fire. Ammo is hard to find. (May cause freezes at the start of stages.
01 - Only one weapon allowed. When you pick up a weapon, you swap for the previous one.
02 - Two weapons allowed (default)
patch=1,EE,105A8D72,extended,00000000

