[Weapon Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Some values may cause freezing depending on the stage. It is possible to carry two of the same weapon. After picking up a second weapon, keep switching between weapons, & after a few switches, you'll wield two of the same gun. Be careful because some stages require you to blast through a door, which requires a specific gun, mots notably at the beginning of Stage 1.
Values - 
00 - DC3 Elite
01 - Spas 12
02 - Walther 2000
03 - Uzi
04 - G36C
05 - AK-47
06 - RPG
07 - M203 
08 - MAC10 Elite
09 - P90
0A - M249
0B - Magnum
0C - M16
0D - Remington 870
0E - Glock
0F - MP5
10 - M16 A2
11 - (NULL) - When aiming, you'll see an AK47, & it will fire, but won't damage enemies
patch=1,EE,005A8D74,extended,00000000